data.description: Come see this lovely 2 story, 2,371sqft home, featuring 3 bedrooms & 2.5 bathrooms with an attached 2 car garage on 0.28 acres. Home is well located in a cul-de-sac next to Farm District Road in Fernley, NV. Mountain views as you look across your backyard! Shopping, schools and entertainment are also close. The yard is fully landscaped and equipped with a fully automatic sprinkler system, as well as RV access/parking in fenced backyard. Large  covered backyard patio. Lovely, pergola above front patio. Interior features a spacious kitchen/dinning room combo and a breakfast bar. Built-in double oven, microwave and refrigerator included. Kitchen also features breakfast bar and island. Living room has gas log fireplace, while floors are a mixture of carpet and ceramic tile throughout the home. Laundry room comes with washer and dryer. Upstairs master bedroom features a walk-in closet, with double sinks, shower stall and double shower heads in master bath. Also upstairs are 2 Jack and Jill style double bedrooms & bathroom. Heated by natural gas and cooled by central A/C. This home is a must see!
